data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: Name three qualities that you think your friends would say you have. Why do you think they would choose these? How do these qualities affect your friendships?
data.answer: I think my friend will describe me as friendly, optimistic, and hardworking. I am friendly and can easily make friends with others. I like to talk with people because good communication skill is the key to any success. As a result, I like to share my happiness and concerns with my friends. I am always optimistic about life. Whenever my friend met difficulties, I will encourage them to cheer up and never give up.（74 字）
